{
  "stem": "14060.8",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we arrived in [INAUDIBLE] lager, this was a camp of about 6,000 or 7,000 people where we have just been replacing 1,500 people who were, unfortunately, sent back to Auschwitz for extermination with an ill transport.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The people in there consisted of Polish people, Hungarians, Romanians.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A mixture of the usual tapestry of European Jews-- only Jews.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were assigned to a factory called Braubach.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's [NON-ENGLISH]-- that was a side branch of I.G.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Farben-- which factory produced synthetic petrols.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, Germany was short of oil and petrol during the war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we-- I myself was working.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was assigned to a group who were building bunkers, concrete bunkers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So my work consisted of carrying cement bags-- at my age-- a full cement bag on my back.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But as I had broad shoulders and I was quite strong, I stood up to the strain.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I found that the only thing which really was sort of weakened me or I found myself very tired is when we went into a night shift.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Even so, the first half of the night, it was OK.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But when it came to the early hours of the morning, that's-- in daybreak is when one has got the least resistance-- I find myself tired, you know.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then during the day, obviously I slept some.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But one doesn't get, during the day, the same rest as otherwise.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And there were appells in between and everything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I mean, it wasn't just a work holiday camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The conditions were [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] not the worst, I would say, from what I hear from other people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The-- some of the kapos behaved terribly badly and were hitting people, as they walked, with sticks for no reason at all.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
